    "TokenAtlas reads macOS Screen Time (the Knowledge database) to see when your coding surfaces and CLI hosts were focused. macOS keeps that file behind Full Disk Access — grant it, then come back to this tab." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
